Epsy Health | Multiple Roles | Remote or onsite | London, UK or Houston, Texas | Full-Time | https://www.epsyhealth.com

Come and help us give the world a better way to live with epilepsy. Epsy is an award winning digital health platform empowering patients, caregivers and healthcare providers in their journey for the treatment of epilepsy. We won the 2020 Google Material Design Award, and two 2021 CES Innovation Awards.

We're looking for Software Engineers and Leaders across a variety of roles, including:

- Senior Back-End engineers;

- Senior Front-end engineer;

- Senior Android;

- Senior QA engineer;

- Senior UX/UI product designer.

Enquiries and applications for all roles: https://www.epsyhealth.com/work-for-us

Bleenco | https://bleenco.com | Software Engineer • Product Owner • Security Engineer • MLOps-DevOps | REMOTE (EU/Europe preferred) • ONSITE (Munich, Germany)

We are a young startup from Munich building a Platform for Situated Workflow Automation in Environment, Health and Safety (EHS). We have a robust and unique technology stack developed in-house alongside paying clients from day one.

If you feel you would like to:

- save human lives and improve working conditions at some of the largest enterprises of our times;

- build a novel streaming technology, own programming language and tools for large scale ML;

Apply at careers@bleenco.com. This is a unique opportunity to be part of the core team from an early stage.
